name: HokieDining
0:
”Alexa, open Hokie Dining.”
”Where can I eat?”
”Alexa, ask Hokie Dining what dining halls are open?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: hokie dining
des: A skill for Virginia Tech Students! Do you ever want food but aren’t sure if a dining hall is open and are too lazy to check the website or brave the weather just to get disappointed? Now you don’t have too! Ask Alexa if specific dining halls are open as well as discover all the currently open dining halls! Never walk to a closed dining hall again!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
